title: Pipestone National Monument: Insects, Spiders, Centipedes, Millipedes
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Animals     Insects, Spiders, Centipedes, Millipedes                Insects, Spiders, Centipedes, Millipedes         Dragonfly NPS, G. Wagner  Over fifty-six families of insects inhabit Pipestone National Monument. Thousands of specimens representing these families are curated at the Monument.
